Source: By tradition, the Psijic Mascot of the order's Ritemaster is always a Bear Cub—but since there's been only one Ritemaster, Iachesis, for over 3,000 years, the tradition hasn't had much opportunity to change. Fortunately, others can befriend them as well!
Target: 전통적으로 결사 의식달인의 시직 마스코트는 항상 아기곰이었습니다. 하지만 이아체시스가 3,000년이 넘도록 유일한 의식달인으로 있게 되면서 그 전통은 바뀔 기회가 별로 없었죠. 다행스럽게도, 다른 사람들도 이 아기곰들과 친구가 될 수 있답니다!

Source: "Even a rugged pioneer of the borderlands can show some distinctive Breton style," says Lady Eloisse of House Manteau. "Our traditional linen shirt is suitable for any occasion!"
Target: 맨토우 가문의 레이디 엘로이스는 이렇게 말합니다. \\"국경 지대에 사는 억센 개척자라도 특유의 브레튼 양식을 보여줄 수 있어요. 우리 전통 아마 셔츠는 어떤 상황에서도 잘 맞는답니다!\"\""

Source: "There's no reason why everyday wear has to look frumpy! A man likes to look good when he's at his trade, and what looks better than a suede doublet over velveteen breeches?" says Lady Eloisse, Couturier of House Manteau.
Target: \\"There's no reason why everyday wear has to look frumpy! A man likes to look good when he's at his trade
column4: and what looks better than a suede doublet over velveteen breeches?\"\" says Lady Eloisse
column5: Couturier of House Manteau."

Source: Lady Eloisse of House Manteau offers this traditional Breton evening dress. As she puts it, "Ostentation is vulgar, but true elegance never goes out of style!"
Target: Lady Eloisse of House Manteau offers this traditional Breton evening dress. As she puts it, \\"Ostentation is vulgar
column4: but true elegance never goes out of style!\"\""

Source: Bretons like to display their wealth through their apparel, as shown by the rich fabric and glistening ornamentation of this outfit designed by Lady Eloisse of House Manteau.
Target: 브레튼은 자신들의 옷을 통해 부유함을 보여주길 좋아합니다. 맨토우 가문의 레이디 엘로이스가 고급 천과 반짝이는 장식을 써서 재단한 이 옷처럼 말이죠.

Source: Lady Eloisse says, "The highborn Breton prefers clothing that is elegant but austere, harkening back to the High Rock tradition of knightly orders, militant but chivalrous. Bright metallic points highlight the buckles and trim."
Target: 레이디 엘로이스는 이렇게 말합니다. \\"상류층 브레튼은 우아하지만 소박한 옷을 좋아한답니다. 기사단의 질서가 자리잡았던 하이 락 전통을 되돌아보면
column4: 전투적이지만 예의가 있었죠. 밝은 금속 장식이 죔쇠와 옷차림을 강조해 준답니다.\"\""

Source: The Black Bear Cub is both playful and affectionate, and is so adorable it's quickly forgiven for whatever trouble it gets into.
Target: 까만 아기 곰은 장난을 좋아하고 애정이 많습니다, 그리고 너무 사랑스러운 나머지 어떠한 문제를 만들더라도 금방 용서받습니다.

Source: The Snow Bear is known for its fierceness, but its cub is as cute as a bug. Maybe even two bugs.
Target: 설원곰은 사납기로 유명하지만, 아기 설원곰은 벌레만큼이나 귀엽습니다. 어쩌면 벌레 두 마리만큼 귀여울지도요.

Source: Lady Eloisse, the designer, says, "A Breton woman likes to add a touch of feminine flair to her otherwise practical clothing. She wants her attire to say she's a lady, no matter what she's doing."
Target: Lady Eloisse, the designer, says, \\"A Breton woman likes to add a touch of feminine flair to her otherwise practical clothing. She wants her attire to say she's a lady
column4: no matter what she's doing.\"\""

Source: The Cave Bear Cub may miss its mountain home, but that just makes it twice as loyal to its mortal companion.
Target: 아기 동굴 곰은 산악지대에 있던 자신의 집을 그리워 하고 있을 지도 모릅니다, 하지만 이는 필멸자 동료에 대한 충성심을 두배로 만들어줍니다.

Source: Originally bred on the Isle of Artaeum, the black-and-white Domino Pig is so smart it can count to five and learn to recognize its name.
Target: 원래 아테이움 섬에서 사육되던 흑백색 도미노 돼지는 정말 영리해서 다섯까지 수를 셀 줄 알며, 자신의 이름을 배우고 알아들을 수 있습니다.

Source: A re-animated Skeletal Bear makes a fearsome mount, and is a favorite of northern Tamriel's necromancers.
Target: 다시 움직이게 된 해골 곰은 무시무시한 탈것이 되어주며, 북부 탐리엘의 강령술사들이 아주 좋아합니다.

Source: Wear Hircine's Gift with pride as the leader of the lycanthrope pack with the Werewolf Lord polymorph. Time to howl!
Target: 늑대인간 군주 변신을 통해 늑대인간 무리의 지도자라는 자랑스런 허씬의 선물을 받아들이세요. 울부짖을 시간입니다!

Source: Mannimarco's Order of the Black Worm must be responsible for the re-animated Zombie Horse, as it was first seen in Cyrodiil as a Worm Anchorite's mount.
Target: Mannimarco's Order of the Black Worm must be responsible for the re-animated Zombie Horse, as it was first seen in Cyrodiil as a Worm Anchorite's mount.

Source: I say! What a jolly chapeau! That's good, solid Coldharbour iron—and at a pinch, one could use it to stew up a fine mulligatawny. Eh?
Target: I say! What a jolly chapeau! That's good, solid Coldharbour iron—and at a pinch, one could use it to stew up a fine mulligatawny. Eh?

Source: The Snow Bear makes a superior mount for northern climes, as it's undaunted by even the fiercest winter weather.
Target: 설원 곰은 북부 지역에서 훌륭한 탈것이 되어 줍니다. 가장 사나운 겨울 날씨 속에서도 흔들림없죠.

Source: The Black Bear is common across Cyrodiil, but is also seen north into High Rock and Skyrim, where it is considered a warrior's mount.
Target: 흑곰은 시로딜 전역에서 흔히 보이지만, 북부의 하이 락과 스카이림에서도 목격됩니다. 이 지역에서는 흑곰을 전사의 탈것이라고 생각합니다.

Source: This costume replicates the armor worn by the scouts of Western Skyrim, in the holds of Haafingar, Whiterun, and Falkreath.
Target: 이 의상은 하핑가르, 화이트런, 팔크리스를 아우르는 서부 스카이림의 정찰병들이 입는 갑옷을 복제한 것입니다.

Source: This costume represents an Akaviri assassin's outfit of mysterious and unknown origin.
Target: 이 의상은 기이하고 알려지지 않은 기원을 가진 아카비리 암살자의 외형을 나타내고 있습니다.

Source: This costume replicates the armor worn by the scouts of Eastern Skyrim, in the holds of the Rift, Eastmarch, and Winterhold.
Target: 이 의상은 리프트, 이스트마치, 윈터홀드를 아우르는 동부 스카이림의 정찰병들이 입는 갑옷을 복제한 것입니다.

Source: This costume replicates the armor worn by Orcish mountain scouts in Skyrim and northern High Rock.
Target: 이 의상은 스카이림과 북부 하이 락의 오크 산악 정찰병들이 입는 갑옷을 복제한 것입니다.

Source: This costume represents the armor worn by the assassins who accompanied the Tsaesci Akaviri invasion.
Target: 이 의상은 츠아에스치 아카비리 침략군에 소속되었던 암살자가 입었던 갑옷을 표현하고 있습니다.

Source: This costume represents the armor worn by the assassins who accompanied the Kamali Akaviri invasion.
Target: 이 의상은 카말리 아카비리 침략군에 소속되었던 암살자가 입었던 갑옷을 표현하고 있습니다.

Source: This costume represents the travel attire of the nomadic Ashlanders of the Mabrigash tribe.
Target: This costume represents the travel attire of the nomadic Ashlanders of the Mabrigash tribe.

Source: This costume replicates the simple but sturdy armor worn by the warriors of the ancient Keptu tribe of Nedes.
Target: 이 의상은 니드 중에서도 고대의 켑투 부족 전사들이 입었던 단순하지만 견고한 갑옷의 복제품입니다.

Source: This costume replicates the armor of the warriors who followed the ancient Nedic king Durac.
Target: 이 의상은 고대의 니딕 왕, 두락을 따랐던 전사들이 입었던 갑옷의 복제품입니다.

Source: This costume represents the hunting clothes of the nomadic Ashlanders of the Mabrigash tribe.
Target: This costume represents the hunting clothes of the nomadic Ashlanders of the Mabrigash tribe.

Source: This costume represents the armor of the nomadic Ashlanders of the Kagesh tribe.
Target: This costume represents the armor of the nomadic Ashlanders of the Kagesh tribe.

Source: Shouldn't an animated skeleton always be a thing of fear and revulsion? This necromantic Pony Guar might change your mind about that!
Target: 움직이는 해골이 언제나 공포스럽고 혐오스러운 것일까요? 이 강령술에 걸린 작은 구아가 당신의 생각을 바꾸어줄지도 모릅니다!

Source: When the Soul-Shriven arrive in Coldharbour, they are garbed in cast-off rags taken from the dead.
Target: 영혼 없는 자들은 콜드하버에 도착했을 때 죽은 사람들의 닳아 해진 넝마를 벗겨내 입었습니다.

Source: When the Soul-Shriven arrive in Coldharbour, some are garbed in cast-off leathers taken from the dead.
Target: 영혼 없는 자들이 콜드하버에 도착했을 때, 몇몇은 죽은 사람들의 닳아 해진 가죽옷을 벗겨내 입었습니다.

Source: When the Soul-Shriven arrive in Coldharbour, some are garbed in cast-off armor taken from the dead.
Target: 영혼 없는 자들이 콜드하버에 도착했을 때, 몇몇은 죽은 사람들의 갑옷을 벗겨내 입었습니다.

Source: With its equine psyche stolen by Daedric magic, the mind-shriven horse is a docile yet terrifying mount.
Target: 데이드릭 마법으로 정신을 도둑맞은 마음 빼앗긴 말은 유순하지만 공포스러운 탈것입니다.

Source: The Red Pit Wolves of southern Skyrim are known for their aggression and ferocity, and you can see that even in their puppies, adorable as they are. They love to play, but that means play-fighting, so expect to get chewed on as you tussle!
Target: 남부 스카이림의 붉은구덩이 늑대들은 공격성과 흉포함으로 유명하며, 그 사랑스러운 새끼들에게서도 같은 모습을 엿볼 수 있습니다. 녀석들은 노는 것을 좋아하지만, 그 노는 것이란 싸움 놀이를 뜻하는 것이니 드잡이를 벌일 때 물리는 것 정도는 각오하세요!

Source: A native of Hammerfell, the Fennec Fox has been domesticated by many of its desert peoples, and makes an alert and loyal pet.
Target: 해머펠 토종 사막여우는 많은 개체가 사막 민족들의 손에 길들여졌고, 기민하며 충성스러운 애완동물이 되었습니다.

Source: The glowing Purple Daggerback boar is found only in Craglorn in the vicinity of the Spellscar, from which it seems to have absorbed some sort of magical aura.
Target: The glowing Purple Daggerback boar is found only in Craglorn in the vicinity of the Spellscar, from which it seems to have absorbed some sort of magical aura.

Source: When a Doom Wolf Pup looks at you with its big red eyes, you may just melt inside—but as soon as you turn your back, that little rascal will be shredding your embroidered Arenthian pillows and digging up your herbal garden.
Target: 아기 파멸 늑대가 커다랗고 붉은 눈동자로 당신을 쳐다보면 당신의 마음은 누그러질지도 모릅니다. 하지만 당신이 뒤돌아서면, 그 자그마한 악동은 곧바로 수놓아진 아렌시안 배게를 찢어버리고 약초 정원을 파헤쳐 놓겠죠.

Source: Common sights around Solitude, these steadfast and fierce wolves also adorn the heraldry of that city. All of them are, of course, good wolves, and befriending one brings you good fortune in the land of the Nords!
Target: Common sights around Solitude, these steadfast and fierce wolves also adorn the heraldry of that city. All of them are, of course, good wolves, and befriending one brings you good fortune in the land of the Nords!

Source: This splendid costume replicates the armor worn by a Centurion of the Imperial Guard, the Emperor's personal bodyguards.
Target: 이 훌륭한 의상은 황제의 개인 경호원들인 제국 근위대의 백부장이 입는 갑옷을 모방한 것입니다.

Source: This costume replicates the armor of a veteran Battemage Tribune, usually the highest ranking Imperial Battlemage to actually take the field and personally engage the enemy.
Target: This costume replicates the armor of a veteran Battemage Tribune, usually the highest ranking Imperial Battlemage to actually take the field and personally engage the enemy.

Source: A denizen of Tamriel's northern shores, the Chub Loon survives on the bounty of the sea, dining on small fish of all types. Though clumsy and awkward on shore, it flies gracefully and is a nimble swimmer. Best of all, they make affectionate pets.
Target: 탐리엘 북부 해안가에서 주로 발견되는 처브 아비새는 바다가 제공해주는 온갖 작은 물고기들을 먹으며 생존합니다. 육지에서는 어설프고 부자연스럽게 행동하지만, 하늘에서는 우아하게 비행하고 물에서는 민첩하게 수영하죠. 가장 멋진 점은 다정한 애완동물이 되어준다는 것입니다.

Source: Behold the Skeletal Horse! Mortal races are not the only creatures that can be re-animated by necromancers. The best part: no need to muck out the stable.
Target: 해골 준마를 보십시오! 강령술로 다시 움직이게 할 수 있는 생명체는 필멸의 종족들 뿐만이 아닙니다. 가장 좋은 점은 마구간을 청소할 필요가 없다는 거죠.

Source: The Skeletal Senche may be the most fearsome of all feline mounts. Expertly re-animated, even in undead form it retains all the lithe strength it possessed in life.
Target: 해골 센치는 모든 고양잇과 탈것들 중에서 가장 무시무시한 존재일지도 모릅니다. 언데드 형상을 하고 있음에도 생전에 가졌던 유연한 힘을 온전히 지닌 채 훌륭하게 다시 움직이죠.

Source: This costume gives the wearer the appearance of those tragic mortals whose will and mentality have been stolen by Molag Bal.
Target: 이 의상은 몰라그 발에게 의지와 지성을 도둑맞고 만 비극적인 필멸자의 모습을 취할 수 있게 해 줍니다.

Source: Your new best friend is a giant blood-sucking insect bloated with pustulant, lethal contagion! It's bursting with both infection and affection—for you!
Target: 당신의 새 절친한 친구는 치명적인 전염성을 가진 농포로 부풀어 오른 거대한 흡혈 벌레입니다! 감염과 애정으로 터질 듯 하죠. 당신을 위해서요!

Source: A Pumpkin Spectre is like a horrific figure from a skooma-induced nightmare! And with this costume, the wearer can take on the semblance of these dread monsters.
Target: 호박 악령은 스쿠마를 빨고 보는 악몽에서 나오는 공포스런 형상처럼 생겼습니다! 이 의상을 입으면 이 공포스런 괴물들의 모습을 취할 수 있습니다.

Source: The naked, grisly smile on the broad skull of the Skeletal Guar mount may be enough to send lesser opponents fleeing in terror when you ride into battle on its creaking, bony frame. The Worm Cult, of course, will just be jealous.
Target: 해골 구아 탈것의 넓적한 해골에 띄워진 노골적이고 소름끼치는 미소는 당신이 그 삐걱거리는 뼈대를 타고 전장으로 달려나갈 때 열등한 적들이 공포에 빠져 도망치게 만들기에 충분할 것입니다. 물론 벌레 교단은 그냥 시샘할 뿐이겠지만요.

Source: The dark magic that makes a spectre animate a scarecrow is thought to be related to those spells that create lurchers from spriggans. Wherever they come from, this costume enables the wearer to appear to be one of these Scarecrow Spectres.
Target: 허수아비를 움직이는 악령을 만들어내는 어둠의 마법은 스프리건에서 러쳐를 만들어내는 주문과 관계가 있다고 여겨집니다. 악령이 어디에서 오건 간에, 이 의상은 착용자가 허수아비 악령의 모습을 취할 수 있게 해 줍니다.

Source: Full-grown echateres may be stubborn and ornery, but the baby Echalettes are playful and, frankly, just plain adorable. Once a young Echalette bonds with its master, it becomes a devoted companion.
Target: 다 자란 에찰테는 고집이 세고 성질도 더러울 지도 모르지만, 아기 에찰테들은 장난기 많고 솔직하며, 말 그대로 사랑스럽습니다. 어린 에찰테가 주인에게 유대감을 가진다면 헌신적인 동료가 되어줄 것입니다.

Source: Donning this costume gives the wearer the guise of one of the Soul-Shriven, Molag Bal's slaves in his Oblivion plane of Coldharbour.
Target: 이 의상을 입으면 몰라그 발의 오블리비언 차원인 콜드하버의 노예, 영혼 없는 자로 가장할 수 있습니다.

Source: "Seeking to meld fire with fungi, Ahzidal created the first Embermould Warhorse. Formed from char morels often used in stews, this mount can light a rider's way on the darkest winter nights."—Halund Greycloak
column4: Ahzidal created the first Embermould Warhorse. Formed from char morels often used in stews

Target: Learned from the Skaal Explorer Outfit Style, acquired from completing Deep Winter Charity Writs during the New Life Festival.

Target: 이 끽끽거리고 악취나는 데이드라 하수인은 당신을 충성스럽게 따를 것입니다. 당신을 위해 싸워주지는 않겠지만요.

Source: An Outfit style that replicates the Mace of Molag Bal Elder Scrolls Artifact, the claymore created by your foe, the Prince of Domination.
Target: An Outfit style that replicates the Mace of Molag Bal Elder Scrolls Artifact, the claymore created by your foe, the Prince of Domination.

Source: Ride a stick mount that symbolizes your fiery dreams of all-consuming doom. Complete with flaming mane, tail, and eyes, this thrice-cursed novelty horse makes your stick-riding experience one for the books … of burning horror!
Target: Ride a stick mount that symbolizes your fiery dreams of all-consuming doom. Complete with flaming mane, tail, and eyes, this thrice-cursed novelty horse makes your stick-riding experience one for the books … of burning horror!

Target: Learned from the Skaal Explorer Outfit Style, acquired from completing Deep Winter Charity Writs during the New Life Festival.

Target: Learned from the Skaal Explorer Outfit Style, acquired from completing Deep Winter Charity Writs during the New Life Festival.

Source: The Copperback variant of the Markarth Bear-Dog is renowned for its responsiveness to training, but keep an eye on it, or will get into all sorts of mischief. Especially keep an eye on its eyes, which are two different colors!
Target: 마르카스 웅견의 변종인 코퍼백 웅견은 훈련에 잘 적응하는 것으로 명성이 높지만, 잘 지켜보지 않는다면 온갖 종류의 나쁜 장난을 칠 것입니다. 특히 그 눈을 잘 지켜보세요. 양 쪽이 서로 다른 색깔을 하고 있으니까요!

Source: Daedric forces have taken the Imperial City, and all three alliances vie to take it back. Experience hours of all-new PvP and PvE gameplay, both above ground and below, plus two new dungeons, never-before-seen monsters, craftable item sets, and more!
Target: 데이드라 군대가 임페리얼 시티를 점령했습니다. 세 세력들은 다시 되찾고 싶어합니다. 수 시간 분량의 새로운 지상과 지하에서 벌어지는 PVP, PVE 경험과 두 개의 던전, 새로운 몬스터, 제작 세트, 그 외에도 새로운 경험이 준비되어 있습니다!

Source: Found throughout Tamriel's northern mountains, the Cave Bear makes a hardy and imposing mount.
Target: 탐리엘의 북부 산악지대 전역에서 발견되는 동굴곰들은 튼튼하고 인상적인 탈것이 되어 줍니다.

Source: The brown Goats of the Dragontail Mountains are stronger than they look. There's a saying in Hammerfell: "Hits as hard as a Dragontail ram!"
Target: The brown Goats of the Dragontail Mountains are stronger than they look. There's a saying in Hammerfell: \\"Hits as hard as a Dragontail ram!\"\""

Source: Learned from the Skaal Explorer Outfit Style, acquired from completing Deep Winter Charity Writs during the New Life Festival.
Target: Learned from the Skaal Explorer Outfit Style, acquired from completing Deep Winter Charity Writs during the New Life Festival.

Source: A goat bred to take part in Daedric rituals? Nonsense. It's just a goat. Isn't it? But why does it look at you like that? And did it just … whisper? No. It's just a goat!
Target: 염소가 데이드릭 의식에 참여하도록 길러진다고요? 말도 안 되죠. 그냥 염소잖아요. 그런데 왜 저렇게 당신을 쳐다보는 걸까요? 그리고 방금... 속삭인 건가요? 아니에요. 그냥 염소라고요!

Source: Who doesn't want to be followed around by a hulking, armored Daedric bug with steel mandibles and a venomous stinger? It eats nothing but the cries and lamentations of your enemies, so it's an easy keeper. Friendly, too—in its way.
Target: 큰 턱에 독침을 가진 커다란 갑옷 입은 데이드릭 곤충과 함께 여행하고 싶지 않은 이가 누가 있을까요? 적들의 비명과 애도만을 먹이로 삼기 때문에 관리하기 쉽습니다. 물론 주인은 잘 따르죠.

Source: Pocket Mammoths were originally bred small in order to make them more manageable as livestock, but in Wrothgar some escaped and began breeding in the wild. However, they're easily domesticated, especially if you get one when it's young.
Target: 포켓 맘모스는 가축으로 기르기 쉽게 하기 위해 개량된 품종입니다. 하지만 로스가에서 몇 마리가 탈주하여 야생에서 번식을 했습니다. 그래도 그들은 길들이기 쉬운 동물입니다. 어릴수록 더 길들이기 쉽죠.

Source: Mastiffs are the most common breed used by the Imperial Legions as battle dogs. The Imperial War Mastiff in particular is the mascot and symbol of the storied Second Legion, headquartered in peacetime in the vicinity of Bruma.
Target: Mastiffs are the most common breed used by the Imperial Legions as battle dogs. The Imperial War Mastiff in particular is the mascot and symbol of the storied Second Legion, headquartered in peacetime in the vicinity of Bruma.

Source: This costume pays tribute to a legendary Nord hero of the Ebonheart Pact. Now you can honor this nameless warrior by adopting his savage appearance.
Target: 이 복장은 에본하트 조약의 전설적인 노드 영웅에게 헌사된 것입니다. 이제 이 이름없는 전사의 맹렬한 모습을 취함으로써 그를 기릴 수 있습니다.

Source: Some followers of Stendarr claim that those who see a Pink Torchbug must perform great acts of charity and mercy by sunset the following day. If they please Stendarr, the pleasant little creature might follow them for a time.
Target: Some followers of Stendarr claim that those who see a Pink Torchbug must perform great acts of charity and mercy by sunset the following day. If they please Stendarr, the pleasant little creature might follow them for a time.

Source: A bloodied Daedric dagger used by a spurned lover. The tears of a victim tormented by Molag Bal. When used in a wicked Icereach coven ritual, they help shape a wicker mount that is worthy of bearing everyone's worst nightmare: you.
Target: A bloodied Daedric dagger used by a spurned lover. The tears of a victim tormented by Molag Bal. When used in a wicked Icereach coven ritual, they help shape a wicker mount that is worthy of bearing everyone's worst nightmare: you.

Source: This costume pays tribute to a legendary Breton hero of the Daggerfall Covenant. Now you can honor this nameless rogue by adopting his intimidating outfit.
Target: 이 복장은 대거폴 동맹의 전설적인 브레튼 영웅에게 헌사된 것입니다. 이제 이 이름없는 불한당의 위협적인 의복을 취하여 그를 기릴 수 있습니다.

Source: Long ago, the secretive Pyre Watch bred local jackals into mounts, allowing them to move swiftly as they patrolled their cursed caverns. Now this nimble and fleet pale steed can be yours!
Target: Long ago, the secretive Pyre Watch bred local jackals into mounts, allowing them to move swiftly as they patrolled their cursed caverns. Now this nimble and fleet pale steed can be yours!

Source: This costume pays tribute to a legendary High Elven hero of the Aldmeri Dominion. Now you can honor this nameless Altmer by adopting her epic appearance.
Target: 이 복장은 알드메리 자치령의 전설적인 하이 엘프 영웅에게 헌사된 것입니다. 이제 이 이름없는 알트머의 서사적인 모습을 취함으로써 그녀를 기릴 수 있습니다.

Source: The night before Waking Day, Iliac Bay Bretons share stories about the Terrible Torchbug of Molag Bal. While the story varies, all agree on one thing: those followed by a cobalt-hued torchbug possess a savagery in battle that haunts any who survive.
Target: The night before Waking Day, Iliac Bay Bretons share stories about the Terrible Torchbug of Molag Bal. While the story varies, all agree on one thing: those followed by a cobalt-hued torchbug possess a savagery in battle that haunts any who survive.

Source: While studying arcane husbandry, Mage Naleldil discovered a long-forgotten Ayleid ritual capable of granting luminescent qualities to common salamanders. Now, due to an unexpected population explosion, she gives them to those who impress her.
Target: While studying arcane husbandry, Mage Naleldil discovered a long-forgotten Ayleid ritual capable of granting luminescent qualities to common salamanders. Now, due to an unexpected population explosion, she gives them to those who impress her.

Source: Some believe that gaining Meridia's favor is like gripping a double-edged blade tightly with bare hands. Yet, if you perform an action she likes, she may gift you with a White Torchbug—perhaps the least worrisome of her favors!
Target: Some believe that gaining Meridia's favor is like gripping a double-edged blade tightly with bare hands. Yet, if you perform an action she likes, she may gift you with a White Torchbug—perhaps the least worrisome of her favors!

Source: Madness follows the Purple Torchbug, or so some claim. Others believe that those who once held Sheogorath's attention attract these insects. Either way, perhaps Sheogorath's dubious blessing touched them.
Target: Madness follows the Purple Torchbug, or so some claim. Others believe that those who once held Sheogorath's attention attract these insects. Either way, perhaps Sheogorath's dubious blessing touched them.

Source: Once this young Netch calf imprints on a master, it will follow him or her anywhere, floating along and tootling happily.
Target: 어린 네치가 주인의 인상을 찍으면, 주인이 어디로 가든 즐겁게 따라갑니다.

Source: Tales have come down to us from the legendary time of the Dragons, when it was said that some Nords were born with Dragon blood in their veins. Now you can wear the look of these legendary Dragon Warriors.
Target: 전설적인 드래곤 시대로부터 전해져오는 이야기에 따르면, 그 당시에는 몇몇 노드들이 드래곤의 피를 가진 채로 태어났다고 합니다. 이제 당신이 그 전설적인 드래곤 전사들의 외형을 취할 수 있습니다.

Source: "One of Ahzidal's experiments involved creating an ideal wolf mount for dangerous forests and caverns. This Fungiflare Wolf has a vicious temperament by design and nature—fungiflare mushrooms are lethal."—Halund Greycloak
Target: \\"One of Ahzidal's experiments involved creating an ideal wolf mount for dangerous forests and caverns. This Fungiflare Wolf has a vicious temperament by design and nature—fungiflare mushrooms are lethal.\"\"—Halund Greycloak"

Source: Xivkyn with exceptional mystical talents are subject to the horrific mental intrusions of the God of Schemes, shattering their mind and making them conduits for his dark visions. The Augurs are chief among these ravaged sorcerers.
Target: 특출난 신비주의적 재능을 가진 지브킨들은 음모의 신이 행하는 끔찍한 정신 침해의 실험체가 되어, 정신이 조각나고 어두운 환시의 전달자가 되게끔 만들어집니다. 예언자들은 그렇게 유린당한 마법사들 중에서도 단연 으뜸입니다.

Source: "Ahzidal made the shadowcap's azure glow the centerpiece of this unsettling feline mount. Prized by spelunkers, this luminescent mount can light up the darkest caverns without making a sound. "—Halund Greycloak
Target: \\"Ahzidal made the shadowcap's azure glow the centerpiece of this unsettling feline mount. Prized by spelunkers

Source: Tormentors are those among the Xivkyn schooled in the anatomies of both mortals and Daedra, studying the arts of inflicting pain over several lifetimes of men and mer.
Target: 지브킨 중에서도 필멸자와 데이드라 양쪽에 대한 해부학 교육을 받은 고문자들은 인간과 머의 일생을 몇 번은 뛰어넘을 고통을 안겨주는 예술의 경지를 연구하고 있습니다.

Source: The goats that come from the ruin of Ninendava in Cyrodiil are no mere domestic livestock. They have long been used in certain forbidden Daedric rituals—and have even been known to lead mortals through those arcane rites.
Target: 시로딜의 니넨다바 유적에서 나오는 염소들은 단순한 사육용 가축이 아닙니다. 이 염소들은 오랫동안 어떤 금지된 데이드릭 의식을 위해 사용되었죠... 그리고 심지어는 필멸자들을 그 불가사의한 의례로 이끌어 간다고도 알려져 있습니다.

Source: Who says a giant, aggressive, blood-sucking insect can't make a loveable pet? Not the Dark Elves of Bal Foyen, who breed them as trackers, watch-hounds, and netch-deflators.
Target: 누가 크고, 공격적이고, 피 빠는 곤충이 사랑스러운 애완동물이 될 수 없다고 말했죠? 발 포옌에서는 통하지 않는 말입니다. 그들은 추적, 경계, 그리고 네치를 수축시키기 위해 이들을 기릅니다.

Source: "Integrating research left behind by Ahzidal the Enchanter, I crafted a bear cub from spores acquired from a well-traveled merchant. This creature bumbles around a bit more than its animal counterpart, but it glows! Perfection!"—Mage Naleldil

Target: 이 의상은 각반이 딸린 메이지 길드 제복의 예시입니다.

Source: "No better companion exists than my devoted Gloomspore Guar Calf. I used spores known for their calming properties to modify the guar's temperament. Regrettably, it makes the creature gassy, but unmatched loyalty is worth opening windows."—Mage Naleldil

Target: 이 의상은 메이지 길드의 정식 로브를 모방한 것입니다.

Source: "Challenged by a colleague, I created a pony-fungus creature. The first few stood as still as statues, so I added manic morels from Dementia. That livened things up considerably. If you adopt one, I suggest keeping it out of your parlor."—Mage Naleldil

Source: Freed at last from her terrible captivity, and rightfully wedded to Jester King Jorunn, the Sovereign Sow can trundle along at your side to share in your adventures. Who would not want a companion of such royal blood and stately countenance?
Target: Freed at last from her terrible captivity, and rightfully wedded to Jester King Jorunn, the Sovereign Sow can trundle along at your side to share in your adventures. Who would not want a companion of such royal blood and stately countenance?

Source: The sound of wind gusting through dusklit, ice-laden trees heralds a Rimedust Indrik's birth. These indriks emanate a sense of deep calm wherever they go.
Target: The sound of wind gusting through dusklit, ice-laden trees heralds a Rimedust Indrik's birth. These indriks emanate a sense of deep calm wherever they go.

Source: The Necrom Ghostgazer is the favored feline companion of Telvanni wizards. They not only keep the skeevers down, but they can "see" intruding demons and spirits.
Target: The Necrom Ghostgazer is the favored feline companion of Telvanni wizards. They not only keep the skeevers down, but they can \\"see\"\" intruding demons and spirits."

Source: "I designed some adorable wolf pups, adding oxblood fungus spores to see if that instills fierce guardianship in them. It worked—they now guard my feet from things like boots and stockings. Consider garbing yourself out of their sight!"—Mage Naleldil
column4: adding oxblood fungus spores to see if that instills fierce guardianship in them. It worked—they now guard my feet from things like boots and stockings. Consider garbing yourself out of their sight!\"\"—Mage Naleldil"

Source: Fierce and courageous fighters, the hunters of Western Skyrim use small packs of these dogs to pursue bears. The Bear-Dogs track, corner, and harry the bears until the hunters can arrive with their spears.
Target: 사납고 용맹한 싸움꾼들인 서부 스카이림의 사냥꾼들은 곰을 추적하기 위해 이 개들로 이루어진 작은 무리를 사용합니다. 웅견들은 사냥꾼들이 창을 가지고 도착할 수 있을 때까지 곰을 추적하고, 몰아가고, 괴롭힙니다.

Source: Dark Elves of House Hlaalu, knowing that Vvardenfell isn't the only place with deadly flora, fauna, and folk, bred a nix-hound that can thrive in different environments. Even with its gorgeous blue-purple shading, it still possesses a menacing air.

Source: Y'ffre's Naming gave all the creatures of Nirn their shapes, even in the arid deserts of Tamriel. When its name comes magically unraveled, then a creature begins to forget its shape and devolve to a state between flora and fauna. Thus the Wild Hunt Camel.

Target: 야생의 사냥 구아는 여명 시대의 혼돈스러운 모습으로 되돌아간 탈것입니다. 식물이 되어버린 부분과 동물인 부분을 모두 가지고 있으며, 혐오스러운 만큼이나 멋진 모습을 하고 있죠.

Source: The Wild Hunt unravels the shapes Y'ffre established for creatures in the Dawn Era, transforming them into monstrous but vigorous hybrid beasts. Among these, both beautiful and abhorrent, is the Wild Hunt Senche-Mount.
Target: 야생의 사냥은 이'프레가 여명 시대에 생명체에게 정해준 모양을 사라지게 하며, 그 동물들을 괴물같지만 활발한 혼합체 짐승으로 변화시킵니다. 그 아름다우면서도 혐오스러운 것들 중에는 야생의 사냥 센치 탈것도 있습니다.

Source: Some say that Hircine meddled with the nature of wolves in a way that made them susceptible to shape-shifting, and from this Daedric interference came both the Werewolf—and the Wild Hunt Wolf. What is the truth of this? Y'ffre knows!
Target: 어떤 이들은 허씬이 늑대의 본질에 어느 정도 간섭해서 늑대들이 모양의 변화에 민감하도록 만들었다고 합니다. 그런 데이드라의 영향력 때문에 늑대인간과 야생의 사냥 늑대가 나타났다고 말이죠. 과연 진실은 무엇일까요? 이'프레만이 아실 겁니다!

Source: It's said that when King Styriche, the Vampire of Verkarth, led his Gray Host west to Bangkorai, his terrible Zombie Hussars were mounted on a great pack of Skeletal Wolves. Some escaped the massacre of the Gray Host, and survived to haunt the wastes.
Target: It's said that when King Styriche, the Vampire of Verkarth, led his Gray Host west to Bangkorai, his terrible Zombie Hussars were mounted on a great pack of Skeletal Wolves. Some escaped the massacre of the Gray Host, and survived to haunt the wastes.

Source: The Ice Wolf of the far north can grow to tremendous size—which is probably why the Nords of Hjaalmarch decided to ride them. Domesticating giant Ice Wolves wasn't an easy task, but it's just the kind of challenge a Nord loves.
Target: The Ice Wolf of the far north can grow to tremendous size—which is probably why the Nords of Hjaalmarch decided to ride them. Domesticating giant Ice Wolves wasn't an easy task, but it's just the kind of challenge a Nord loves.

Source: When the Wood Elves invoke the Wild Hunt, creatures forget their Y'ffre-taught shapes and shift into unnatural forms. Such are the Wild Hunt Horses, mounts that occupy a space between flora and fauna.
Target: 우드 엘프들이 야생의 사냥을 불러일으킬 때면, 생명체들은 이'프레가 가르쳐 주었던 모양새를 잊고 비정상적인 형태로 변한다고 합니다. 식물과 동물 사이의 자리를 차지하는 탈것인 야생의 사냥 말처럼 말입니다.

Source: The brown Highland Wolf is common in the Colovian hills and in Cyrodiil's Great Forest, where wild packs are feared by farmers and shepherds. But foresters have domesticated the beasts and, bred for size, use them as mounts.
Target: The brown Highland Wolf is common in the Colovian hills and in Cyrodiil's Great Forest, where wild packs are feared by farmers and shepherds. But foresters have domesticated the beasts and, bred for size, use them as mounts.

Source: Bred for size and savagery from the fierce timber wolves of the southern Jerall Mountains, the Doom Wolf has been adopted as the mount of choice by the secretive and deadly Dark Brotherhood.
Target: 덩치와 흉포함을 길러가며 사육되는 제랄 산맥 남부의 맹렬한 산림늑대들은 파멸 늑대라고 불립니다. 이들은 비밀스럽고 치명적인 다크 브라더후드의 탈것으로 선택받았습니다.

Source: When warrior-dos are "bent" into dro-m'Athra, they become that fearsome variety the Khajiit call a do-m'Athra.
column4: they become that fearsome variety the Khajiit call a do-m'Athra."

Source: The guards of Abah's Watch dress lightly during the heat of the day, or when they know they're going to have to run down a fleeing perpetrator.
Target: The guards of Abah's Watch dress lightly during the heat of the day, or when they know they're going to have to run down a fleeing perpetrator.

Source: Possibly the most feared of the dro-m'Athra are their spellcasters, the jo-m'Athra, Khajiiti wizards who became "bent" into Lost Cats.
Target: Possibly the most feared of the dro-m'Athra are their spellcasters, the jo-m'Athra, Khajiiti wizards who became \\"bent\"\" into Lost Cats."

Source: The dar-m'Athra are the stealthiest of the dro-m'Athra, and therefore rarely seen, except for a final glimpse as one kills you.
Target: The dar-m'Athra are the stealthiest of the dro-m'Athra, and therefore rarely seen, except for a final glimpse as one kills you.

Source: The Abah's Watch opens the armor locker and gears up whenever a pirate ship ties up at the docks, because they know there's going to be trouble in the taverns and mayhem in the market.
Target: 항구에 해적선이 정박하면 아바의 감시자들은 사물함을 열어 중무장을 합니다. 술집과 시장에서 문제가 일어나 소요 사태가 일어난다는 사실을 알기 때문입니다.

Source: The common or Kindlespit Dragon Frog is an engagingly preposterous little pal whose antics never fail to amuse. Hammerfell tales say the huge Dragons of ancient legend were all turned into these tiny flame-puffing hoppers.
Target: The common or Kindlespit Dragon Frog is an engagingly preposterous little pal whose antics never fail to amuse. Hammerfell tales say the huge Dragons of ancient legend were all turned into these tiny flame-puffing hoppers.

Source: Come nightfall temperatures drop in the Landing, and Abah's Watch armors up for its night patrols. The alleys of town are dangerous after dark.
Target: 저녁이 되어 부두의 온도가 떨어지면 아바의 감시자들은 야간 순찰을 위해 중무장을 합니다. 어두운 도시의 골목길은 위험합니다.

Source: Ready for piratical action? You will be in this basic sea rover attire, which gives you plenty of opportunity to show off your buccaneer body art. Avast, and prepare to repel boarders!
Target: Ready for piratical action? You will be in this basic sea rover attire, which gives you plenty of opportunity to show off your buccaneer body art. Avast, and prepare to repel boarders!

Source: Wear this full pirate rig along with a fierce scowl, and no one will dare lay a hand on your booty. Suitable whether you're swaggering into a dockside tavern, sharpening your cutlass at the gangplank, or just hanging around the port looking dangerous.
Target: Wear this full pirate rig along with a fierce scowl, and no one will dare lay a hand on your booty. Suitable whether you're swaggering into a dockside tavern, sharpening your cutlass at the gangplank, or just hanging around the port looking dangerous.

Source: The slug-like Sloads of Thras bred the flame-hued Tangerine Dragon Frog so they could be spotted more easily in their archipelago's murky lagoons. Some say they were bred to be pets, but the Sload word for them translates as "snacks."
Target: The slug-like Sloads of Thras bred the flame-hued Tangerine Dragon Frog so they could be spotted more easily in their archipelago's murky lagoons. Some say they were bred to be pets, but the Sload word for them translates as \\"snacks.\"\""

Source: The comical Blue Oasis Dragon Frog is native to Hew's Bane, and before they were bred as pets could be found only on that Hammerfell peninsula. These little bug-eaters are popular mascots at open-air taverns.
Target: 우스꽝스럽게 생긴 푸른 오아시스 드래곤 개구리는 휴의 베인에 서식하는 생물입니다. 애완동물로 사육되기 전에는 해머펠 반도에만 있었습니다. 벌레를 먹는 이 생물은 야외 술집의 마스코트로 인기가 있습니다.

Source: This warrior's costume is clothing of the savage Winterborn, a clan of raiders from the Reach who have invaded Orsinium.
Target: 오시니움을 침략한 리치 출신의 야만 부족 윈터본의 전사가 입는 의복입니다.

Source: A mix of metal and leather melded with the hide of a great snow bear, fashioned to pay tribute to Malacath, the Furious One.
Target: A mix of metal and leather melded with the hide of a great snow bear, fashioned to pay tribute to Malacath, the Furious One.

Source: This shaman's costume is clothing of the savage Winterborn, a clan of raiders from the Reach who have invaded Orsinium.
Target: 오시니움을 침략한 리치 출신의 야만 부족 윈터본의 주술사가 입는 의복입니다.

Source: This hunter's costume is clothing of the savage Winterborn, a clan of raiders from the Reach who have invaded Orsinium.
Target: 오시니움을 침략한 리치 출신의 야만 부족 윈터본의 사냥꾼이 입는 의복입니다.

Source: A mix of metal and leather melded with the hide of a great brown bear, fashioned to honor Trinimac, the warrior god.
Target: A mix of metal and leather melded with the hide of a great brown bear, fashioned to honor Trinimac, the warrior god.

Source: A mix of metal and leather melded with the hide of a great black bear, fashioned in the ancient style of the Orsimer.
Target: A mix of metal and leather melded with the hide of a great black bear, fashioned in the ancient style of the Orsimer.

Source: This stalwart mount comes from the ashlands downwind of the volcanoes of the Velothi Mountains, and is well adapted to surviving under the harshest of conditions.
Target: This stalwart mount comes from the ashlands downwind of the volcanoes of the Velothi Mountains, and is well adapted to surviving under the harshest of conditions.

Source: The white camel is said to be sacred to Zeht, the Redguard god of food and farming. The devout folk of Hammerfell bow when a Cloud Camel rides past.
Target: 음식과 농업의 신인 제츠가 신성시한 흰 낙타입니다. 독실한 신앙을 가진 해머펠 사람은 구름 낙타가 지나갈 때 절을 합니다.

Source: Most riders consider Black Camels to be creatures of bad luck and misfortune. But if you're a thief riding off into the night with your ill-gotten gains, you might see things differently.
Target: 대다수의 기수들은 검은 낙타를 불운의 상징으로 여깁니다. 하지만 당신이 저녁에 장물을 실은 채로 달리는 도둑이라면, 이 낙타가 다르게 보일겁니다.

Source: The Moonlight Senche-Tigers have been the sleek and silvery guardians of the Khajiiti temples of the moons ever since the revelation of the Riddle'Thar.
Target: 달빛 센치 호랑이들은 리들타르의 계시 이래로 줄곧 카짓의 달들 사원을 지키는 날렵한 은빛의 수호자가 되었습니다.

Source: This is the stoic, hard-working beast that riders in the wastes of Hammerfell count on to survive. And if things come to a fight, it's just plain mean.
Target: This is the stoic, hard-working beast that riders in the wastes of Hammerfell count on to survive. And if things come to a fight, it's just plain mean.

Source: Come to the homeland of the Orcs in ESO's first new PvE quest content DLC! Help King Kurog rebuild the city of Orsinium, and watch its walls and towers rise due to your deeds. Includes new armor, weapons, a solo challenge arena, and more!
Target: 엘더스크롤 온라인의 첫 번째 PVE 퀘스트 콘텐츠 DLC, 오크들의 고향으로 오십시오! 쿠로그 왕을 도와 오시니움 도시를 재건하고, 당신의 행동으로 도시의 성벽과 탑들이 일어서는 모습을 지켜보십시오. 새로운 방어구, 무기, 일인용 아레나, 그 외에도 더 많은 것들이 포함되어 있습니다!

Source: Every member of the Vosh Rakh religious movement hides his or her identity behind a golden mask of Orcish visage patterned after Trinimac's own auric-tinged skin.
Target: Every member of the Vosh Rakh religious movement hides his or her identity behind a golden mask of Orcish visage patterned after Trinimac's own auric-tinged skin.

Source: This variant of the Bear-Dog is a favorite of the Markarth Watch—and of the thieves who attempt to evade them. The Watch uses them to sniff out trouble, while the outlaws employ them to keep an eye out for the Watch!
Target: 이 변종 웅견은 마르카스 감시대가 아주 좋아하는 동물입니다. 감시대를 피하려는 도둑들도 좋아하죠. 감시대원들은 문젯거리를 찾아내려고 웅견을 이용하고, 무법자들은 감시대가 오는지 살펴보려고 웅견을 이용하거든요!

Source: The greenish, or "Mossy" Netches, are most commonly found in the West Gash region of northwest Vvardenfell. The calves are docile, even for Netches, and will happily follow along behind anyone who smells of their favorite fungi.
column4: are most commonly found in the West Gash region of northwest Vvardenfell. The calves are docile
column5: even for Netches
column6: and will happily follow along behind anyone who smells of their favorite fungi."

Source: For the Orc who aspires to impress, this season Borzighu of Coldsnap Clothiers offers rich fabrics in subtle shades, accented with gold and steel to convey an indelible image of wealth and power.
Target: For the Orc who aspires to impress, this season Borzighu of Coldsnap Clothiers offers rich fabrics in subtle shades, accented with gold and steel to convey an indelible image of wealth and power.

Source: With a nod to tradition but clearly fashioned with the new sensibilities of a reinvigorated Orsinium in mind, the crown and armor of the Orsimer King makes a definite statement about strength, unity, and honor.
Target: 오시머 국왕의 왕관과 방어구는 힘과 통합 그리고 명예를 나타내는 상징으로, 노드의 전통 복장이지만 오시니움의 밝고 활기찬 감성을 새롭게 담아내도록 만들어졌습니다.

Source: In Orsinium these days, even the busiest tusker likes some flair in his clothing—and nothing says "modern Orc" like a bias-cut-placket tunic from Borzighu at Coldsnap Clothiers. "This outfit," he says, "is one for the ages!"
Target: 요즘 오시니움에서는 가장 바쁜 엄니쟁이조차도 옷을 세련되게 입기를 좋아합니다. 반짝한파 의류점의 볼지구가 어슷끊기로 옆이 트이도록 재단한 튜닉을 입은 \\"최신식 오크\"\"는 말할 것도 없고요. 볼지구는 이렇게 말합니다. \"\"이 옷은 후세에 길이 남을 작품이라고!\"\""

Source: For the stylish town Orc, Borzighu the Tidy Tailor of Orsinium has decided the watchwords this season are "restrained elegance." As he puts it, "Strut your Orcish heritage with style!"
Target: For the stylish town Orc, Borzighu the Tidy Tailor of Orsinium has decided the watchwords this season are \\"restrained elegance.\"\" As he puts it

Source: "It may be small, but at least it's gloomy. And if you enjoy beating up on your friends, like I do, it's right next door to the arena!" —Goorguk gro-Murtag, Orcish Realtor
column4: but at least it's gloomy. And if you enjoy beating up on your friends
column5: like I do
column6: it's right next door to the arena!\"\" —Goorguk gro-Murtag
column7: Orcish Realtor"

Source: It may be small but it's solid, and it keeps the sandstorms out. The scenery is magnificent, but if you're in the mood for civilization, it's right outside the south gate of Hallin's Stand.
Target: 이 집은 작을지 모르지만 견고하며 또한 모래 폭풍도 막아 줍니다. 풍경도 훌륭하지만 만약 문명을 느끼고 싶은 기분이 들 경우, 이 집은  할린의 저항 남문에서 가깝습니다.

Source: After the death of his beloved daughter Haruzeh at the Running of the Dunerippers, the Magnifico Z'za retired to his house in Sentinel and never spoke again, spending his last days playing endless games of hammergammon with his trained monkey, Lizard.
Target: 사랑하는 딸 하루제가 듄리퍼의 질주로 죽은 후 귀인 즈'자는 센티넬의 집에 눌러 앉아 두번 다시는 이야기 하지 않았습니다. 그의 마지막 나날들을 훈련된 원숭이인 리자드를 상대로 오로지 해머감몬 게임을 하며 지냈다고 합니다.

Source: This fortified household is strong, intimidating, and remote—in short, everything an Orc holds dear. And if you get tired of the "remote" part, there's a convenient wayshrine just outside your gate!
Target: This fortified household is strong, intimidating, and remote—in short, everything an Orc holds dear. And if you get tired of the \\"remote\"\" part
column4: there's a convenient wayshrine just outside your gate!"

Source: When Hakkvild drove the Orcs of Yashnag's Kingdom out of Falkreath in 2E 467, the exiled Orsimer came east to establish Forsaken Stronghold. But the last Orcs died in 563 after they were visited by a merchant infected with Knahaten Flu.
Target: 하크빌드가 2시대 467년에 야스나그 왕국의 오크를 팔크리스에서 몰아냈을 때 추방된 오시머는버려진 요새를 설립하기 위해 동쪽으로 왔습니다. 그러나 최후의 오크는 크나헤이튼 열병에 감염된 상인이 방문한 후 563년에 사망했습니다.

Source: Before Daggerfall Castle was built, the kingdom's rulers lived in this imposing manor, now known as Daggerfall Overlook. The keep comes complete with a lower dungeon level.
Target: 대거폴 성이 세워지기 이전에는, 왕국을 지배자들은 대거폴 감시대이라고 알려져있는 이 인상적인 저택 안에서 살았었습니다. 이 성채에는 지하 감옥이 있습니다.

Source: A magnificent castle keep, complete with walls, watchtowers, well, fountain, and stable, all dramatically sited on the slopes of an active volcano! It just needs a murder, and then it will be haunted as well.
Target: 장대한 성의 보루, 벽, 감시탑, 약수터, 분수, 마굿간이 있고, 이 모두가 활화산의 경사면에 자리 잡고 있습니다. 이제 살인 사건과 귀신만 있으면 완벽한 것이죠.

Source: This elegant pleasure palace, with its walled grounds enclosing stables, well, gardens, pool, watchtower, and docks, were paid for by the blood and treasure spilled from the countless treasure ships taken by the legendary Captain Izad.
Target: 이 우아한 궁궐에는 벽으로 둘러싸인 마굿간, 약수터, 정원, 연못, 감시탑, 부두가 있습니다. 전설의 이자드 선장이 피를 흘리며 빼앗은 배의 셀 수 없는 보물로 만들었다고 합니다.

Source: Set in a quiet corner of Reaper's March, the rural manor of Serenity Falls deserves its name, with plenty of room for servants and livestock, all behind a handsome wall to keep out the bandits and burglars.
Target: 리퍼스 마치의 조용한 구석에 자리잡은 세레니티 폭포의 시골 저택은 하인과 가축을 위한 충분한 공간이 있으며, 도둑과 절도범을 막을 멋진 벽이 있습니다.

Source: You probably think only the mad masterminds of vast criminal organizations have their own private tropical islands. Well, think again: you, too, could have a hidden hideaway ever-trembling on the verge of volcanic destruction!
Target: 방대한 범죄 조직의 미친 지도자들만이 열대 섬을 소유하고 있다고 생각할 것입니다. 자, 다시 생각해보죠. 당신도 역시 화산 폭발 일보직전에 있는 늘 흔들리는 숨겨진 은신처를 가질 수 있습니다!

Source: All your friends are already nearby in Rawl'kha, yes? Invite them over to have a party at your so-sleek riverside house, with its private garden and over-creek deck. Much sweetness!
Target: 친구가 모두 라울카 근처에 살고 있습니까? 개인 정원과 도크가 있는 멋진 냇가의 집에 초대해서 파티를 합시다. 멋지네요.

Source: Ah, such a sweet estate, with every appurtenance—out in the country, yet convenient to the nearby Khajiiti metropolis of Dune! What can one do but love and admire it?
Target: 이 어찌 아름다운 저택인가, 카짓의 대도시 듄에서도 가깝습니다! 사랑스러울 수 밖에 없지 않나요?

Source: This capacious Dunmeri mansion, with its walled garden and view across a waterfall to majestic Mournhold, was originally built to house a noble family of House Indoril.
Target: 담벼락이 있는 정원과 장엄한 모운홀드 폭포가 건너보이는 이 널찍한 던메리 맨션은 원래 인도릴 귀족 가문의 거처를 제공하기 위해 지어졌습니다.

Source: A small elevated house on an idyllic plantation in the mild and hospitable clime of Khenarthi's Roost? This one would find that sweet paradise!
Target: 케나티의 횃대의 포근하고 쾌적한 기후에 있는 목가적인 농장에 위치한 고상한 작은 집이라고요? 이 카짓이 그 달콤한 낙원을 찾아내야겠군요!

Source: This fortified manor between Arenthia and Skingrad at the headwaters of the Strid River should satisfy all those who aspire to the life of the landed gentry. Inside the gatehouse you'll find gardens, a waterfall, and a mansion in Second Empire style.
Target: 스트리드 강 상류 아렌시아와 스킨그라드 사이에 있는 이 요새화된 저택은 지주의 삶을 동경하는 사람의 희망을 모두 만족시켜 줍니다. 수위실 앞에는 정원, 폭포, 제 2 제국 스타일의 집을 볼 수 있습니다.

Source: In the heart of The Rift, just outside the lively, small town of Nimalten, you will find this sturdy wooden home, with a large hearth to keep you warm in the Skyrim winter, and a stone wall to keep out the trolls.
Target: 리프트 중심부에 위치한 활기 넘치는 작은 마을인 니말텐 교외에서 이 튼튼한 목조 주택을 발견할 것입니다. 스카이림의 겨울에도 따뜻하게 지켜주는 큰 난로와 트롤들을 막을 수 있는 돌담이 있습니다.

Source: An Imperial, of course, is at home anywhere in Tamriel. This compact house at the Baandari Trading Post in Malabal Tor is a bit of Cyrodiil in Valenwood, and just steps away from the fine food and drink at the Silver Moons Inn.
Target: 임페리얼은 물론 탐리엘의 어느 곳에서도 집에 있습니다. 발렌우드의 시로딜 일부 지역인 말라발 토르의 반다리 교역소에 있는 이 작은 집은 단지 한 두 걸음 떨어져 있는 은빛 달 여관에서 좋은 음식과 음료를 즐기기에 편리합니다.

Source: No one has seen Phrastus the Scholar since his ill-advised return to the Imperial City. He's probably fine—he must be!—but in the meantime, his walled town house in Elinhir is available on an indefinite basis.
Target: 임페리얼 시티로 돌아가도록 심각한 조언을 받은 이래로 학자 페라스투스를 본 사람은 없습니다.  그는 아마도 무사할 것입니다. 반드시요! 하지만 그 동안 엘린히어에있는 벽으로 둘러싸인 그의 도시 주택을 무기한으로 쓸 수 있습니다.

Source: Fine urban living in Windhelm is now available at this commodious town home, which features a lofty main floor, two fireplaces, and a second-floor balcony. Alas, that balcony lacks a railing, which is how Grymharth, after too much mead, came to woe.
Target: 윈드헬름의 멋진 도시 생활은 고풍스러운 메인 층, 두개의 벽난로 및 2층 발코니를 갖춘 이 널찍한 도시 주택에서 가능합니다. 아아, 저 발코니에는 난간이 없습니다. 그림하스가 많이 취한 후 화를 당한 곳이죠.

Source: By tradition, the biggest mansion on the south side of Riften is always called Mistveil Manor. Since the death of old Thane Snelgar, the current Mistveil Estate has come available, including its impressive stone mansion with attached stable.
Target: 전통적으로 리프튼 남부에서 가장 큰 저택은 항상 안개장막 저택이라고 불려 왔습니다. 늙은 테인 스넬가가 죽은 후 사람의 거주가 가능해졌죠. 인상적인 석조 저택을 포함한 안개장막 영지가 새로운 주인을 찾고 있습니다.

Source: How does this spacious and comely hilltop manor, so far above the fen, nonetheless stay so delightfully damp? It is a paradox, like life itself. (Don't miss the upper-story lodging with separate entrance!)
Target: 이 광활하고 멋진 언덕 저택은 늪에서 떨어져 있지만 어떻게 기분좋게 보습이 될까요? 이 수수께끼는 마치 생명의 신비 같습니다. (윗층 셋방에 별도의 입구가 있다는 것을  놓치지 마세요!)

Source: A perfect graht-oak pod home, grown by a Home Singer from the very roots of Elden Root—compact, comfortable, and convenient to everything. Praise Z'en!
Target: 엘든 루트의 바로 그 뿌리에서 자라난 완벽한 그랏-참나무 꼬투리 집입니다. 아담하고, 편안하며, 모든 것에 편리하죠. 젠'을 찬양하라!

Source: "This house is a good house, plenty of room for guar! Palisade is strong to keep guar from straying, and many guar can feed in the garden! Very good, yes! Esqoo will come to visit often!" —Esqoo of Dhalmora
column4: plenty of room for guar! Palisade is strong to keep guar from straying
column5: and many guar can feed in the garden! Very good
column6: yes! Esqoo will come to visit often!\"\" —Esqoo of Dhalmora"

Source: The famous Breton merchant-explorer Captain Margaux hasn't been seen since her ship the Golden Spriggan sailed off over the horizon into the Sea of Pearls—which makes her house near the docks in Daggerfall available for you!
Target: 저명한 브레튼 상인이자 탐험가였던 마가욱스 선장은 황금 스프리건 호를 타고 진주해로 나간 이래로 모습을 감추었습니다. 이제 대거폴에 있는 그녀의 집을 얻을 기회가 왔습니다.

Source: Two floors, no waiting, in this handsome walled town house makes for prime real estate in the quaint Rivenspire town of Fell's Run. The local story that the ravens that loiter around the front steps are the revenant spirits of former owners is absurd.
Target: 이 멋진 벽으로 둘러싸인 대합실 없는 2층 주택은 진기한 리븐스파이어 마을인 펠의 여정에서 최고의 부동산으로 손꼽힙니다. 현지의 소문에 의하면 계단 주위를 날아다니는 까마귀들은 이전 집주인들의 망령이라고 합니다. 말도 안 되는 소리죠.

Source: When civilization grows too confining, it's a relief to be able to withdraw into a handsome home in the wilds—especially one with an imposing wall around it, to keep out beasts and bandits.
Target: 문명의 이기들이 답답하게 느껴진다면,  거친 들판의 멋진 집에 틀어박혀있는 것도 좋습니다. 압도적인 벽들이 주위를 둘러싸고 있어, 야수나 산적을 쫓을 생각이라면 더할 나위가 없죠.

Source: The Gorinir family, a cadet branch of the royal Camoran line, has fallen on hard times and had to sell their palatial Cormount home. The seasons turn, luck changes, and their loss is your gain.
Target: 카모란 왕가로부터 분가하여 떨어져나온 고리니르 가문은 금전적 어려움에 자신들의 대궐같은 코마운트 저택을 매물로 내놓아야만 했습니다. 계절이 돌고, 행운이 바뀌어 이제 그들의 손실은 당신의 이익이 되었습니다.

Source: This charming abode was named after both the Prophet Veloth who founded the surrounding town of Narsis, and the Velothi Mountains that rise above the walled garden at its rear.
Target: 이 멋드러진 거주지의 이름은 이 거주지가 있는 도시 나르시스를 설립한 벨로스와 담벼락이 쳐진 정원 뒤에 있는 벨로시 산맥의 이름을 따서 지어졌습니다.

Source: The Gardners were the royal family of Wayrest before every single one of them was carried off by the Knahaten Flu. Which is why the spacious and well-situated Gardner House feels like it's fit for a king!
Target: 가드너 가문은 크나헤이튼 열병으로 인해 몰살당하기전까지는 웨이레스트의 왕가였습니다. 그게 바로 광활하고 좋은 입지를 가진 이 가드너 가옥이 왕에게 어울릴 것 같은 이유죠!

Source: This residence might not be in Kragenmoor's best neighborhood, but if you're looking for classic Dunmeri architecture at an affordable price, this town house certainly fits the bill.
Target: 이 거주지는 크라겐무어 최고의 거주지라고 할 수는 없지만, 던메리 양식의 건물을 저렴한 가격에 구매하려 한다면 이 도시 주택은 충분히 합리적인 선택일 것입니다.

Source: As the least restricted seaport in the Summerset Isles, Vulkhel Guard has visitors from across Tamriel—and you're likely to meet most of them hoisting a mug at the Mara's Kiss Pub.\nRoom is too small for Dueling.

Source: Brown and black leather armor topped with a black leather cowl, like that worn by Breton Skirmisher Scouts.

Source: The migratory Monarch Butterfly is a common sight across all of southern Tamriel, and it's seen in the northern provinces during summer. The Monarch is said to represent the souls of the present, in contrast to the Ancestor Moth that represents the past.
Target: 이주성이 있는 제왕나비는 남부 탐리엘 전역에서 흔히 보이는 생명체이며, 여름 동안에는 북부 지방에서도 모습을 드러냅니다. 전해지는 말에 따르면, 이 제왕나비들은 현재의 영혼을 상징한다고 합니다. 과거를 상징하는 선조 나방들과는 대조적으로 말이죠.

Source: "The Jerboas, you say? Ah, yes, the little jumping skeevers with the so-big ears. There are many in the Ashen Scar, and if you catch one when it's small, it makes for a pleasant, fuzzy friend. I had one when I was a kitten!" —Shuzirri of Riverhold
column4: 그래. 엄청 커다란 귀를 달고서 이리저리 뛰어다니는 쬐끄만 스키버들 말이군. 잿빛 흉터에 많이 있지. 쬐끄만 녀석을 잡는다면 재밌고 보송보송한 친구가 되어줄거야. 나도 야옹이였을 때 한 마리 갖고 있었지!\"\" —리버홀드의 수지리"

Source: Most Argonians live above ground, where the sun can shine on the leaves of their Hists, but some, strange and reclusive, live in subterranean caverns. Over time their scales grow as pale as marsh mist.
Target: Most Argonians live above ground, where the sun can shine on the leaves of their Hists, but some, strange and reclusive, live in subterranean caverns. Over time their scales grow as pale as marsh mist.

Source: The Dead-Water Tribe of Naga Argonians are a spiky lot to begin with, and when they want to look tough, they just pile on more spikes. This trick works for just about anyone, really.
Target: The Dead-Water Tribe of Naga Argonians are a spiky lot to begin with, and when they want to look tough, they just pile on more spikes. This trick works for just about anyone, really.

Source: It's said that a warrior of the Dead-Water Tribe saw the impressive sideburns on a Breton general and decided it was a look that could be improved upon with Jaw-Fins. Wise decision.

Source: The legend among the underworld explorers of the Undaunted is that these little incendiary sprites are responsible for lighting all the candles, torches, and lanterns found burning underground, flying ahead of adventurers to ignite them in the dark.
Target: The legend among the underworld explorers of the Undaunted is that these little incendiary sprites are responsible for lighting all the candles, torches, and lanterns found burning underground, flying ahead of adventurers to ignite them in the dark.

column4: I was assigned by Larnatille to breed an appropriate mount for our sages to ride upon when working in the field. I proudly present my result: the loyal and majestic senche-serval!\"\" —Corderil of Sunhold"

Source: Those doing darker deeds, such as practicing the art of Necromancy, might wish to have their attire reflect their interests. Dealing with the control and animation of the spirits and bodies of the deceased can take its toll on an average garment.

Source: True, it does hiss rather than meow, and has shiny scales rather than soft fur, but otherwise the Senche-Lizard Cub is just as adorable as any other kitten.

Source: The Wolf-Lizard Pup is simply adorable when it tries to howl, just hisses instead, and looks ever so confused.
Target: The Wolf-Lizard Pup is simply adorable when it tries to howl, just hisses instead, and looks ever so confused.

Source: Though you know it's just going to grow up and become big, dumb, scaly livestock, how can you resist those lizard-calf eyes?
Target: Though you know it's just going to grow up and become big, dumb, scaly livestock, how can you resist those lizard-calf eyes?

Source: Most Echalettes are docile and fawn-like, but not the Badger Ruff breed, which are strangely fierce and irritable. They're so ornery they've been known to chase away inquisitive Sabre Cats.
Target: Most Echalettes are docile and fawn-like, but not the Badger Ruff breed, which are strangely fierce and irritable. They're so ornery they've been known to chase away inquisitive Sabre Cats.

Source: This smaller breed of Haj Mota lurks in the brackish estuaries of Black Marsh's southern coast, camouflaged by the gray color of the murky tidewater. When hand-raised from hatching, they make surprisingly pleasant pets.
Target: This smaller breed of Haj Mota lurks in the brackish estuaries of Black Marsh's southern coast, camouflaged by the gray color of the murky tidewater. When hand-raised from hatching, they make surprisingly pleasant pets.

Source: A Haj Mota is an ambush predator, waiting patiently in concealment until its prey should come into attack range. The Verdigris breed tends to hide in algae-covered pools where its color acts as camouflage.
Target: A Haj Mota is an ambush predator, waiting patiently in concealment until its prey should come into attack range. The Verdigris breed tends to hide in algae-covered pools where its color acts as camouflage.

Source: Though the adult Bear-Lizards can be quite intimidating, even fearsome, the roly-poly lizard cubs are disarmingly cute. (For reptiles, that is.)
Target: Though the adult Bear-Lizards can be quite intimidating, even fearsome, the roly-poly lizard cubs are disarmingly cute. (For reptiles, that is.)

Source: When young Argonian egg-siblings tell their creche-parents they want a pony, this is what they mean. And now that you've seen it, don't you want one, too?

Source: Non-Wood Elves might think it strange that Bosmeri Pod-Singers, who magically persuade Valenwood trees to grow into houses, wear clothes entirely made of animal leather and quills, but such is the mandate of the Green Pact.
